Mara opens the door with a sour face.
"What is it, now?" she asks.
"Did you bring me what I asked for?"
"I believe I did," you say, showing her the bra of the purest white.
"Impressive," says Mara. She takes her bra and throws it onto her bed. "Well, a deal is a deal. And now I'll tell you my flatmate's nickname."

"Nickname? What about the real name?" you protest.
"The nickname is all you get, take it or leave it."
"Okay..."

"So. His nickname is 'The Knob," says Mara.
"Knob?" you ask. "Does it, by any chance, have anything to do with the shape of his penis?"
"Get out." Mara shuts the door on your face.

So! You know that the dude's nickname is 'The Knob.' You also know, from the list of names at the back of the photo, that 'Knob' belongs to Carlos Rodriguez. This can only mean that... Yes! You are not that hangover. You put 2 + 2 together.

The dude next door is called Carlos!
